author: chamikara
msg: Client side is working for a single message.
Sandesha recommends the users to use call.invokeNonBlocking with useSeperateTransport=true for in-out calls.
If they use invokeBlocking it may time out quickly (defined by InOutMepClient.timeOutInMilliSeconds). Usually RM interactions take some time.
